org.openbel.framework.api
Class BasicPathFinder

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.api.BasicPathFinder
All Implemented Interfaces:
PathFinder
public class BasicPathFinder
extends Object
implements PathFinder

Implements a basic PathFinder implementation with a max depth constraint.

The max search depth constraint default is defined at DEFAULT_MAX_SEARCH_DEPTH. To override this constraints create with BasicPathFinder#BasicPathFinder(int).

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>
